{
  "stem": "4967.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They established a big Jewish hospital in the main ghetto, and a hospital in the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I frequently, I used to visit the small ghetto to visit friends or relations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The atmosphere in the ghetto was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Rumors came that the Germans were burning the people in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Crematoriums had been built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And also, they established ghettos in Latvia and Estonia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And by the way, they took people from our ghetto, in 1942 or 43, and sent them to Estonia and Latvia, which was a very hard camps.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They worked the people very hard, and the food was bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, the Germans used to come in, used to surround the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They used to come into the ghetto and take away just people at random.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And the life carried on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We had electricity.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We had water supplies, which we didn't pay for it because the Germans stopped paying for the labor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And, and the ghetto became smaller.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We had to move further back inside the ghetto because people has been liquidated, taken away to other places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And the Germans decided to make the ghetto smaller.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And life carried on, very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Especially in winter, there was no timber, no wood to make a fire, although every house, every flat had a fireplace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So we decided to dismantle the fences and any furniture and make it as firewood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we survived 1942 and 43.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And I think in 1942, '43, there was a big action.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And they took away half of the ghetto been liquidated at the forts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I got a special certificate, a work certificate, stating that I, Reuben Drehspul is employed in the workshops in the ghetto under a sewing machine mechanic.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
